      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention project seekers and restoration fans! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it is currently in poor condition and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a rewarding rebuild. If you love a hands-on challenge, this is the perfect budget-friendly start for your next big automotive project!",
